    "description": "<p> </p>  <p><strong>ZAFFERANO ITALIAN RESTAURANT & LOUNGE</strong></p>  <p>Zafferano is a chic contemporary Italian restaurant, bar and lounge.  Located on the 43rd storey of the Ocean Financial Centre along Singapore CBD’s bustling Collyer Quay, Zafferano offers an uninterrupted panoramic view of the island and the Marina Bay waterfront.  Zafferano is Italian for ‘Saffron’.</p>  <p><strong>Cuisine</strong></p>  <p>Zafferano offers an authentic Italian menu focusing on creating dishes using the highest quality fresh ingredients, observing the style of traditional Italian cuisine while incorporating a modern touch.</p>  <p> </p> ",
